title: RECAP: No. 11 Tech knocks off No. 20 Texas in Austin - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: RECAP: No. 11 Tech knocks off No. 20 Texas in Austin - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: Bryson Williams had 17 points and six rebounds while Clarence Nadolny scored 14 to help lead No. 11 Texas Tech to a 61-55 win over No. 20 Texas on Saturday at the Frank Erwin Center. The Red Raiders (21-6, 10-4 Big 12) swept the regular-season series over the Longhorns (19-8, 8-6 Big 12) for the second straight year and have now won four in a row in Austin after holding UT to only 28.3 percent shooting.
